{
  "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "一张照片动辄几百万像素，为什么存成文件却小得多？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "秘密就藏在离散余弦变换里，简称 DCT。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.33,
      "size": 21312,
      "text": "它是 JPEG 图像压缩的数学核心。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "basis",
      "line_id": "basis-1",
      "filename": "basis-basis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/basis-basis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "任何一段信号，都可以写成一系列不同频率余弦波的叠加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "basis",
      "line_id": "basis-2",
      "filename": "basis-basis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/basis-basis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "低频余弦缓慢起伏，勾勒信号的大轮廓。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "basis",
      "line_id": "basis-3",
      "filename": "basis-basis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/basis-basis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "高频余弦快速震荡，负责补上细节和棱角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "coeff",
      "line_id": "coeff-1",
      "filename": "coeff-coeff-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/coeff-coeff-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "DCT 算出每个余弦基的权重，也就是一串系数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "coeff",
      "line_id": "coeff-2",
      "filename": "coeff-coeff-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/coeff-coeff-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "对平滑信号来说，能量几乎全都集中在最左侧的低频系数上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "coeff",
      "line_id": "coeff-3",
      "filename": "coeff-coeff-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/coeff-coeff-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "右侧那些高频系数往往很小，接近于零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "compress",
      "line_id": "comp-1",
      "filename": "compress-comp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/compress-comp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "既然高频系数很小，我们干脆把它们丢掉，只留前几个。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "compress",
      "line_id": "comp-2",
      "filename": "compress-comp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/compress-comp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "用逆变换把保留的系数还原，重建信号几乎和原来一模一样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "compress",
      "line_id": "comp-3",
      "filename": "compress-comp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/compress-comp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "存储的数字少了一大半，这就是有损压缩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "试着调整保留的系数个数，看重建曲线如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "保留越少压缩率越高，曲线也会慢慢丢掉细节变得平滑。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "DCT 把信号分解成余弦基，能量集中在低频。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "丢掉微小的高频系数，就能在几乎不失真的前提下大幅压缩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "discrete-cosine-transform",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/discrete-cosine-transform/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "一组余弦波，撑起了整个数字图像世界，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
